    <div class="bakuchiol-footer__body">
      <div class="bakuchiol-footer__text">
        <p>
          Crafted for every skin type, the Bakuchiol Skin collection combines clean, vegan ingredients with the power of bakuchiol to reveal smoother, brighter, more luminous skin. A modern, gentle approach to age-defying skincare.

